    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "> Should we deep clone the object before sending it to transformData ?\n\nShould not be needed since every render re-computes fresh data, so the data is not yet passed to any other widget.\n\n> How to handle the multiple templates widgets (e.g. hits) ? This could be an idea:\n\nYes `transformData` (instead of transformsData) and mapping to the templates.$KEY should be allright.\n\nAlso with #115 we will soon no more have single 'template' but 'templates' everywhere.\n",
